<FILEID>AP-NR-04-20-88 0422EDT</FILEID>
<1ST_LINE>r p PM-CongressionalCaucus-List     04-20 0184</1ST_LINE>
<2ND_LINE>PM-Congressional Caucus-List,200</2ND_LINE>
<HEAD>With PM-Congressional Caucus</HEAD>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Here are the 43 senators who will be attending
the Democratic National Convention, July 18-21, in Atlanta as
``super delegates,'' and their choice for the nomination:
</TEXT>
<HEAD>Michael Dukakis (13)</HEAD>
<TEXT>
