   Jordan's Crown Prince El Hassan Ibn Talal and his
wife, Crown Princess Sarvath, met Wednesday with Emperor Hirohito
at the Imperial Palace, officials said.
   Hassan was the second foreign dignitary to meet the 86-year-old
emperor since September when he underwent abdominal surgery.
