   Bond prices slipped and interest rates rose in an erratic
session.
   The dollar moved marginally higher against all major currencies
except the Canadian dollar in light trading.
   Grain and soybean futures prices rallied, energy futures
retreated, precious metals were mixed and livestock and meat were
mostly higher.
